HEADWORD: Marriageable
<hw>Mar"riage*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fit for, or
capable of, marriage; of an age at which marriage is allowable.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Mar"riage*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

